==English==
===Noun phrase===
'''[[fish]] [[tank]]'''

A general term which describes a container, usually made out of glass or acrylic, specifically designed for holding water and marine life. Typically: turtles, fish, corals and plants.

A fish tank setup, which can involve a combination of the above is usually called an [http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/aquarium aquarium].


